snippet.title: Piecewise Functions - How to Evaluate
snippet.description:
Learn how to evaluate piecewise functions in this free math video tutorial by Mario's Math Tutoring.  We discuss what a piecewise function is and how to solve given an x-value.

0:09 Example 1 
0:35 Analyzing Which Equation to Use in the Piecewise Function
2:14 Example 2
